OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The US actor Bill Hayes, who starred in
OL,6, the soap opera Days of Our Lives for   
OL,7, more than five decades, has died at the
OL,8, age of 98.                             
OL,10,FHe first portrayed the character of    
OL,11,FDoug Williams in 1970 and also met his 
OL,12,Fwife, the actress Susan Seaforth Hayes,
OL,13,Fwhile filming the series.              
OL,15,FLast June, he celebrated his 98th      
OL,16,Fbirthday on the set of the American    
OL,17,Fdaytime soap surrounded by co-stars.   
OL,19,FHis agent told the BBC he died on      
OL,20,FFriday surrounded by family.           
